{"id":8656,"date":"2025-09-23T06:22:13","date_gmt":"2025-09-23T06:22:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/realtrips.in\/?post_type=trip&#038;p=8656"},"modified":"2025-11-27T12:20:45","modified_gmt":"2025-11-27T12:20:45","slug":"maldives","status":"publish","type":"trip","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/trip\/maldives\/","title":{"rendered":"MALDIVES"},"content":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":8824,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","destination":[111],"activities":[],"trip_types":[76],"difficulty":[],"trip_tag":[],"wptravelengine_custom_taxonomy_tripcategory":[78],"class_list":["post-8656","trip","type-trip","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","destination-ultimate-maldives","trip_types-customized-international-tour","tripcategory-customized-international-tour"],"packages_ids":[8657],"trip_extras":[],"cut_off_time":{"enabled":false,"duration":0,"duration_unit":"days"},"booked-seats":[],"code":"WTE-8656","price":115777,"has_sale":false,"sale_price":0,"discount_percent":0,"currency":{"code":"INR","symbol":"&#8377;"},"duration":{"days":5,"nights":4,"duration_unit":"days","duration_type":"days"},"min_pax":1,"max_pax":"","discount_value":0,"discount_label":"&#8377;0 Off","primary_category":27,"available_times":{"type":"default","items":["2021-1-01","2021-2-01","2021-3-01","2021-4-01","2021-5-01","2021-6-01","2021-7-01","2021-8-01","2021-9-01","2021-10-01","2021-11-01","2021-12-01"]},"description":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Escape to a tropical haven where turquoise waters meet powdery white sands and endless horizons. Stay in luxurious overwater villas, dive into vibrant coral reefs, enjoy sunset cruises, and indulge in world-class spa retreats. Perfect for honeymoons, romantic getaways, or serene holidays, the Maldives is the ultimate blend of beauty, luxury, and tranquility.<br><br><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->","cost_includes":"Return Economy Airfare BOM-BOM \nAccommodation on FB basis \nBreakfast Lunch Dinner + Room \nRound trip airport transfer by Speed Boat  \nAirport assistance on arrival and departure \nAll applicable taxes and service charge for above services \nWelcome drinks on arrival. \nA Bottle of Water 500ml per person per day to be placed in the room.","cost_excludes":"Any meals other than those mentioned above included. \nSport activities \/Moterable activities  \nAirfare \nGST 5% \nAny portage at airports and hotels, tips, insurance, wine, mineral water, telephone charges, and all Items of personal nature. \nAny services not specifically mentioned in the inclusions. \nExpenses caused by factors beyond our control like rail and flight delays, roadblocks, vehicle mal-Functions, political disturbances etc.                    ","itineraries":[],"faqs":[{"title":"1. What is included in the Maldives package? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Resort stay, airport transfers (often by speedboat or seaplane), daily meals, and selected activities depending on the package.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"2. Do Indian travelers need a visa for the Maldives?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>No, Indians get a free visa on arrival for up to 30 days.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"3. What type of accommodation is available? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Choices range from beachfront villas to luxury overwater bungalows with private pools.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"4. What activities can I enjoy in the Maldives? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Snorkeling, scuba diving, dolphin watching, sunset cruises, water sports, and spa experiences.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"}],"is_featured":false,"featured_image":{"width":374,"height":226,"file":"2025\/09\/maldives-1.png","filesize":141519,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"maldives-1-300x181.png","width":300,"height":181,"filesize":29001,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/w